locs.text: prati ghante stok jaanakaaree praapt karata hai
laghu kampanee prateek
apanee alphavantagai api kunjee darj karen
krpaya apanee api kunjee pradaan karen.
pradarshan api kunjee ka upayog nahin kiya ja sakata.
aapakee api kunjee 16 varnon kee honee chaahie.
stok deta praapt karate samay koee truti huee. atirikt jaanakaaree yahaan paee ja sakatee hai
shuruaatee stok keemat
uchch stok keemat
kam stok keemat
band stok keemat
stok volyoom
api kunjee aavashyak hai. setings se konfigar karen.
koee stok deta upalabdh nahin hai.
yah anubhaag aapako stok konfigar karane deta hai.
api kunjee
alphavantagai stok api ke lie kunjee
kampanee kod
stok kampanee
setings pravishtiyaan praapt karane mein viphal.
stok jaanakaaree nahin mil sakatee.
stoks kya hain?
stoks kee jaanakaaree kya hai, yah bataata hai

stoks kisee kampanee ke stok prais ka enaalisis hai jo kampanee stoks detaabes mein rajistard hai, jaise ki nasdaq ka rajistard kampanee detaabes. jaise hee har rajistard kampanee ke stok prais badalate hain, ham aapako aapakee chunee huee kampanee, jaise ki nasdaq, dow jonais, vagairah ke stok prais kee har ghante kee histree dete hain.
stoks kee jaanakaaree ko kaise proses karen?
stoks kee jaanakaaree ko samajhane ke proses ke baare mein baat karata hai

intaraiktiv tui aapako us khaas kampanee ke baare mein stoks kee jaanakaaree deta hai jise aap traik kar rahe hain, jaise ki opaning aur klojing stok prais, haee aur lo stok prais, aur doosaree jaanakaaree. har ghante, yah jaanakaaree badalatee hai, isalie aapako kampanee ke stok prais kaisa paraphorm karate hain, isakee gaharee samajh paane ke lie prais ko jitana ho sake kareeb se dekhana hoga.
